<p>Х║╗ 1 Д╦╜И─╩Х╬▒Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀Г └Х╬⌠Е┤╨Г╩⌠Ф·°Д╦▌Д╧▀Е┴█Г └Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓Х╬⌠Е┤╨Г └Г╩⌠Ф·°Ф≤╞Г╠╩Д╪╪Г └Ц─┌Д╬▀Е╕┌О╪▄ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Д╪╟Х╝║Г └Е┤├Г║╝Ф─╖Е▐╞И─ Х©┤Х╝║Г╝≈Ф═┤Е┤├Х╞╞Ф²╔Х║║И┤▐Ц─┌Х║╗ 1 Д╦╜Г └ $Z$ Г╩÷Х╝║И┤▐Е▓▄Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀Х╬⌠Е┤╨Г └ $t$ Г╩÷Х╝║И┤▐Г └Д╫°Г■╗Ф≤╞Д╦─Ф═╥Г └О╪▄Е╕┌ $\beta_1$ Г └ $Z$ Г╩÷Х╝║И┤▐Г╜┴Д╨▌ $\hat \beta_1 / SE(\hat \beta_1)$Ц─┌Е╫⌠ $Z$ Г╩÷Х╝║И┤▐Г └Г╩²Е╞╧Е─╪Е╬┬Е╓╖Ф≈╤О╪▄Х╞╢Ф≤▌И⌡╤Е│┤Х╝╬ $H_0: \beta_1=0$ Д╦█Ф┬░Г╚▀Ц─┌И⌡╤Е│┤Х╝╬Д╧÷Е╟╠Ф≤╞ $p(X)=\frac{e^{\beta_0}}{1+e^{\beta_0}}$О╪▄Х║╗Г╓╨ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">default</code> Ф╕┌Г▌┤Д╦█Д╬²Х╣√Д╨▌ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">balance</code>Ц─┌Г■╠Д╨▌Х║╗ 1 Д╦╜ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">balance</code> Г └ p Е─╪Е╬┬Е╟▐О╪▄Е⌡═Ф╜╓Ф▀▓Г╩² $H_0$О╪▄Х║╗Ф≤▌ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">default</code> Ф╕┌Г▌┤Д╦▌ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">balance</code> Д╧▀И≈╢Г║╝Е╝·Е╜≤Е°╗Е┘ЁГЁ╩Ц─┌Е▐╕Е╓√О╪▄Х©≥И┤▄Ф┬╙Х╥²И║╧Д╪╟Х╝║И─ Е╦╦Ф└▐Д╧┴Д╦█Е╓╖О╪▄Д╦╩Х╕│Д╫°Г■╗Ф≤╞Х╟┐Х┼┌Е╧ЁЕ²┤Ф▀÷Е░┬Ф╕┌Г▌┤Д╫©Д╧▀Д╦▌Г°÷Е╝·Ф∙╟Ф█╝Е╝·И≥┘ odds Ф⌡╢Ф▌╔Х©▒Ц─┌</p>

<h3 id="33-И╒└Ф╣▀">3.3 И╒└Ф╣▀</h3>

<p>Е╞╧Д╨▌Ф÷░Д╦╙Д©║Г■╗Е█║Д╫≥И╒² <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">balance</code> Д╦╨ $1000$ Г╬▌Е┘┐Г └Д╦╙Д╫⌠О╪▄Е┘╤Д╪╟Х╝║Г └Х©²Г╨╕ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">default = YES</code> Ф╕┌Г▌┤Ф≤╞Е╓ Е╟▒О╪÷</p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\hat p(X)=\dfrac{e^{\hat \beta_0 + \hat \beta_1 X}}{1+e^{\hat \beta_0 + \hat \beta_1 X}}=\dfrac{e^{-10.6513 + 0.0055\times 1000}}{1+e^{-10.6513 + 0.0055\times 1000}}=0.006</script>

<p>Е╞╧Д╨▌ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">balance</code> Д╦╨ $2000$ Г╬▌Е┘┐Г └Д╦╙Д╫⌠Е▒╒О╪÷</p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\hat p(X)=\dfrac{e^{\hat \beta_0 + \hat \beta_1 X}}{1+e^{\hat \beta_0 + \hat \beta_1 X}}=\dfrac{e^{-10.6513 + 0.0055\times 2000}}{1+e^{-10.6513 + 0.0055\times 2000}}=0.586</script>

<p>Е▐╞Х╖│О╪▄Е╞╧Д╨▌Ф÷░Д╦╙Д╦╙Д╫⌠О╪▄Д©║Г■╗Е█║Д╫≥И╒² (<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">balance</code>) Х╤┼И╚≤О╪▄Е┘╤Х©²Г╨╕ (<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">default = YES</code>) Г └Ф╕┌Г▌┤Д╧÷Х╤┼И╚≤Ц─┌</p>

<p>Е▐╕Е╓√О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Х©≤Е▐╞Д╩╔Е╟²Х╞∙Г■╗Е╝ Ф─╖И╒└Ф╣▀Е▐≤И┤▐ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student</code> Ф²╔Ф▀÷Е░┬И─╩Х╬▒Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀Ц─┌Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е╟├ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student</code> Г╪√Г═│Д╦╨Д╦─Д╦╙Х≥ Ф▀÷Е▐≤И┤▐ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student [YES]</code>О╪ Е╜╕Г■÷Д╦╨ $1$О╪▄И²·Е╜╕Г■÷Д╦╨ $0$Ц─┌Х║╗ 2 Г╩≥Е┤╨Д╨├Г■╗ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student</code> И╒└Ф╣▀ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">default</code> Ф╕┌Г▌┤Г └И─╩Х╬▒Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀Г └Г╩⌠Ф·°О╪▄Е▐╞Д╩╔Г°▀Е┤╨Х≥ Ф▀÷Е▐≤И┤▐Г └ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Е─╪Ф≤╞Ф╜ёГ └О╪▄Е┘╤ p Е─╪Д╧÷Ф≤╞Ф≤╬Х▒≈Г └Ц─┌Х©≥Х║╗Ф≤▌Е╜╕Г■÷Ф╞■И²·Е╜╕Г■÷Ф⌡╢Е╝╧Ф≤⌠Х©²Г╨╕Ц─┌</p>

<p><span style="font-size:10pt"> <span style="color:steelblue;font-weight:bold">Х║╗ 2</span>О╪ Е°╗ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Default</code> Ф∙╟Ф█╝Д╦╜О╪▄Е╩╨Г╚▀Г■╗ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student</code> И╒└Ф╣▀ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">default</code> Ф╕┌Г▌┤Г └И─╩Х╬▒Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀Г └ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Д╪╟Х╝║Ц─┌<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student</code> Г■╗Д╦─Д╦╙Х≥ Ф▀÷Е▐≤И┤▐ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student [YES]</code> Г╪√Г═│О╪▄$1$ Д╩ёХ║╗Е╜╕Г■÷О╪▄$0$ Д╩ёХ║╗И²·Е╜╕Г■÷Ц─┌</span></p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>б═</th>
      <th style="text-align: center">ГЁ╩Ф∙╟</th>
      <th style="text-align: center">Ф═┤Е┤├Х╞╞</th>
      <th style="text-align: center">$Z$ Г╩÷Х╝║И┤▐</th>
      <th style="text-align: center">p Е─╪</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Intercept</code></td>
      <td style="text-align: center">$-3.5041$</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">$0.0707$</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">$-49.55$</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">$&lt; 0.0001$</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student [YES]</code></td>
      <td style="text-align: center">$0.4049$</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">$0.1150$</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">$3.52$</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">$0.0004$</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\widehat{\Pr}(\texttt{default}=\texttt{YES} \mid \texttt{student}=\texttt{YES})=\dfrac{e^{-3.5041+0.4049\times 1}}{1+e^{-3.5041+0.4049\times 1}}=0.0431</script>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\widehat{\Pr}(\texttt{default}=\texttt{YES} \mid \texttt{student}=\texttt{NO})=\dfrac{e^{-3.5041+0.4049\times 0}}{1+e^{-3.5041+0.4049\times 0}}=0.0292</script>

<p>Е▐╞Д╩╔Г°▀Е┬╟О╪▄Е╜╕Г■÷Ф╞■И²·Е╜╕Г■÷Х©²Г╨╕Ф╕┌Г▌┤Ф⌡╢Е╓╖Ц─┌</p>

<h3 id="34-Е╓ Е┘┐И─╩Х╬▒Е⌡·Е╫▓">3.4 Е╓ Е┘┐И─╩Х╬▒Е⌡·Е╫▓</h3>

<p>Г▌╟Е°╗Х─┐Х≥▒И╒└Ф╣▀Д╦─Д╦╙Д╨▄Е┘┐Е⌠█Е╨■Е▐≤И┤▐Е▐≈Е╓ Д╦╙Е⌡═Г╢═Е╫╠Е⌠█Г └Ф┐┘Е├╣Ц─┌Г╠╩Д╪╪Д╨▌Д╧▀Е┴█Г └Е╓ Е┘┐Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е▐╞Д╩╔Е╟├Д╨▄Е┘┐И─╩Х╬▒Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф▌╗Е╧©Е┬╟Е╓ Е┘┐Ф┐┘Е├╣О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\log \left(\dfrac{p(X)}{1-p(X)}\right)=\beta_0 + \beta_1 X_1 + \cdots + \beta_p X_p</script>

<p>Х©≥И┤▄О╪▄$X=(X_1,\dots,X_p)$ Х║╗Г╓╨ $p$ Д╦╙И╒└Ф╣▀Е▐≤И┤▐О╪▄Х©≥Г╖█Ф┐┘Е├╣Д╦▀О╪▄И─╩Х╬▒Е┤╫Ф∙╟Д╦╨О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">p(X)=\dfrac{e^{\beta_0 + \beta_1 X_1 + \cdots + \beta_p X_p}}{1+ e^{\beta_0 + \beta_1 X_1 + \cdots + \beta_p X_p}}</script>

<p>Е▓▄Д╧▀Е┴█Д╦─Ф═╥О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е▐╞Д╩╔И─ Х©┤Ф°─Е╓╖Д╪╪Г└╤Ф√╧ФЁ∙Д╪╟Х╝║ГЁ╩Ф∙╟ $\beta_0,\beta_1,\dots,\beta_p$Ц─┌</p>

<p>Х║╗ 3 Г╩≥Е┤╨Д╨├Г■╗ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">balance</code>Ц─│<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">income</code> Е▓▄ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student</code> Д╦┴Д╦╙И╒└Ф╣▀Е▐≤И┤▐Е╞╧ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">default</code> Ф╕┌Г▌┤Е╩╨Г╚▀Г └И─╩Х╬▒Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀Г └ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Д╪╟Х╝║Ц─┌</p>

<p><span style="font-size:10pt"> <span style="color:steelblue;font-weight:bold">Х║╗ 3</span>О╪ Е°╗ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Default</code> Ф∙╟Ф█╝Д╦╜О╪▄Г╩⌠Е░┬ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">balance</code>Ц─│<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">income</code>Ц─│<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student</code> Д╦┴Д╦╙И╒└Ф╣▀Е▐≤И┤▐Е╩╨Г╚▀Г └И╒└Ф╣▀ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">default</code> Ф╕┌Г▌┤Г └И─╩Х╬▒Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀Г └ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Д╪╟Х╝║Ц─┌<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student</code> Г■╗Д╦─Д╦╙Х≥ Ф▀÷Е▐≤И┤▐ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">student [YES]</code> Г╪√Г═│О╪▄$1$ Д╩ёХ║╗Е╜╕Г■÷О╪▄$0$ Д╩ёХ║╗И²·Е╜╕Г■÷Ц─┌<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">income</code> Г └Е█∙Д╫█Д╦╨Е█┐Г╬▌Е┘┐Ц─┌</span></p>

